descriptionHtml:
Saturday is the best way to FIND YOUR PEOPLE!

Saturday makes it fun and easy to find your people. Create and join private groups on Saturday to chat, see who’s around, and keep in touch with friends, colleagues, classmates, and other like-minded people.

Here’s how it works:

*SATURDAY GROUPS
- Members in each group appear on your map
- Your map updates as you swipe between your groups enabling you to easily see where other group members are located
- All Groups contain private group chats, “hangout” functionality to easily meet up in real life, sharing options, and member lists with user profiles
- Groups are private and contain robust privacy controls - users must be invited in order to join and group owners can require admin approval for new members to join
- All users automatically begin with default groups for 'friends’ and their 'college year.'

*ROBUST PRIVACY CONTROLS
Want to hide your online status or precise location? No problem - you can disclose as much or as little information as you're comfortable with!

*SERENDIPITY WITH OUR UNIQUE HANGOUT FEATURE
Want to grab coffee or see who’s around to grab dinner? Posting a hangout on Saturday is just 1-click away. See who's around and watch the magic happen.

*FIND OUT WHEN FRIENDS ARE TRAVELING OR VISITING NEARBY
Open the app and instantly discover which of your friends are traveling & nearby.

*MAKE FRIENDS IN A NEW CITY
Saturday makes it really easy to meet new people when moving to or traveling in a new city.

*CONNECT WITH CLASSMATES
Instantly see where classmates from your college and class year are hanging out.

*LINK YOUR PROFILE TO SNAPCHAT, INSTAGRAM & TIKTOK
Connecting with new friends is now super simple and fun - just add your social media handles.

🔥 SATURDAY IS IDEAL FOR:
- Staying in touch with your loose connections
- Digital Nomads and Travelers
- Professional Groups and Colleagues
- Connecting with other attendees at Conferences
- Interest-based Groups (ie - Runners, Singles, Dog Lovers, Happy Hour fans)
- Influencers
- Any connected group of like-minded people

Saturday is 100% Free. Serendipity is just seconds away...
